Deployment Instructions:

- Unzip the file contents.
- Run "mvn package"
	- Compiles code.
	- Runs unit tests
	- Deploys the code in an embedded container in Random port (SlackDeploysAppApplicationTests.java)
	- Runs Integration tests, hitting the REST endpoints using HTTP and validates.
	- Builds slack-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
- Run "java -jar target/slack-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar"
- Start hitting the REST API endpoints


API 3: Retrieve All engineers in the data set

*** Browser - http://localhost:8080/engineers
*** Terminal - curl -X GET 'http://localhost:8080/engineers'
*** Content-Type: application/json

